name: Spaghetti with Tomato Sauce
ingredients: pasta, tomato sauce, salt, pepper, oil
directions: Boil pasta. Heat sauce with salt, pepper, and oil. Mix pasta with sauce and serve.

name: Chicken Fried Rice
ingredients: chicken, rice, egg, soy sauce, oil, peas, corn
directions: Cook chicken in oil. Scramble eggs. Add rice, peas, corn, and soy sauce. Mix everything and serve.

name: Fruit Smoothie
ingredients: banana, strawberry, milk, sugar
directions: Blend banana, strawberries, milk, and sugar until smooth. Serve cold.

name: Omelette
ingredients: egg, salt, pepper, oil
directions: Beat eggs with salt and pepper. Heat oil in pan, pour eggs, cook until set. Fold and serve.

name: Grilled Chicken Salad
ingredients: chicken, lettuce, tomato, oil, salt, pepper
directions: Cook chicken with oil, salt, and pepper. Chop lettuce and tomato. Combine all and serve.

name: Chocolate Chip Cookies
ingredients: flour, sugar, chocolate chips, butter, egg
directions: Mix flour, sugar, butter, egg, and chocolate chips. Spoon onto baking tray. Bake at 350°F for 12-15 min.

name: Garlic Butter Shrimp
ingredients: shrimp, garlic powder, butter, salt, pepper
directions: Melt butter in pan, add garlic powder, shrimp, salt, and pepper. Cook until shrimp turns pink. Serve.

name: Banana Pancakes
ingredients: banana, egg, flour, sugar, butter
directions: Mash banana, mix with egg, flour, and sugar. Cook spoonfuls in buttered pan until golden.

name: Chicken Tacos
ingredients: chicken, tortilla, salt, pepper, paprika
directions: Cook chicken with salt, pepper, and paprika. Place in tortillas and serve.

name: Fruit Salad
ingredients: apple, banana, berries, honey
directions: Chop all fruits and mix. Drizzle with honey and serve.

name: Buttered Noodles
ingredients: pasta, butter, salt, pepper, garlic powder
directions: Cook pasta, drain, mix with butter, salt, pepper, and garlic powder. Serve warm.

name: Grilled Cheese Sandwich
ingredients: bread, cheese, butter
directions: Butter bread slices, place cheese between them. Grill until golden brown. Serve hot.

name: Chicken Noodle Soup
ingredients: chicken, pasta, carrots, peas, salt, pepper
directions: Cook chicken, add pasta, carrots, and peas. Season with salt and pepper. Simmer and serve.

name: Mango Smoothie
ingredients: mango, milk, sugar
directions: Blend mango, milk, and sugar until smooth. Serve chilled.

name: Mashed Potatoes
ingredients: potatoes, butter, salt, pepper, milk
directions: Boil potatoes until soft. Mash with butter, milk, salt, and pepper. Serve warm.

name: Lemon Pepper Chicken
ingredients: chicken, lemon, pepper, salt, garlic powder, oil
directions: Marinate chicken with lemon, pepper, salt, garlic powder, and oil. Bake or pan-cook until done.

name: Banana Berry Bowl
ingredients: banana, berries, honey
directions: Slice banana and mix with berries. Drizzle with honey. Serve fresh.

name: Shrimp Skillet
ingredients: shrimp, oil, garlic powder, paprika, salt, pepper
directions: Heat oil, add garlic, paprika, salt, pepper, and shrimp. Cook until shrimp is done. Serve.

name: Beef and Potato Skillet
ingredients: ground beef, potatoes, onion powder, garlic powder, oil
directions: Cook beef with onion and garlic powder. Add diced potatoes. Cook until potatoes are soft. Serve hot.

name: Baked Salmon
ingredients: salmon, oil, lemon, salt, pepper
directions: Brush salmon with oil, season with salt, pepper, and lemon. Bake at 375°F for 15-18 min. Serve.

name: Cinnamon Apples
ingredients: apple, butter, honey, cinnamon
directions: Cook sliced apples with butter, honey, and cinnamon until soft. Serve warm.

name: Lemon Butter Broccoli
ingredients: broccoli, butter, lemon, salt, pepper
directions: Steam broccoli. Toss with melted butter, lemon juice, salt, and pepper. Serve.

name: French Toast
ingredients: bread, egg, milk, sugar, cinnamon, butter
directions: Mix eggs, milk, sugar, cinnamon. Dip bread and cook in buttered pan until golden. Serve.

name: Peanut Butter Banana Toast
ingredients: bread, peanut butter, banana, honey
directions: Toast bread, spread peanut butter, add banana slices and drizzle honey. Serve

name: Simple Beef Tacos
ingredients: ground beef, tortilla, salt, pepper, paprika, garlic powder
directions: Cook beef with seasonings. Serve in tortillas with optional toppings.

name: Chicken Stir Fry
ingredients: chicken, peas, corn, carrots, soy sauce, oil, salt, pepper
directions: Cook chicken in oil, add vegetables, season with soy sauce, salt, and pepper. Serve hot.

name: Berry Yogurt Bowl
ingredients: yogurt, berries, honey
directions: Mix yogurt with berries and honey. Serve fresh.

name: Baked Chicken Wings
ingredients: chicken wings, oil, salt, pepper, paprika, garlic powder
directions: Season wings, drizzle with oil, bake at 400°F until cooked. Serve hot.

name: Fruit Yogurt Smoothie
ingredients: yogurt, banana, berries, sugar
directions: Blend all ingredients until smooth. Serve chilled.

name: Chicken Wrap
ingredients: chicken, tortilla, lettuce, tomato, pepper, oil
directions: Cook chicken, place in tortilla with lettuce and tomato. Roll and serve.

name: Shrimp Pasta
ingredients: pasta, shrimp, butter, garlic powder, salt, pepper
directions: Cook pasta, sauté shrimp with butter and garlic. Mix with pasta and serve.

name: Beef Rice Bowl
ingredients: ground beef, rice, salt, pepper, garlic powder
directions: Cook beef with seasonings. Serve over cooked rice.

name: Lemon Chicken Pasta
ingredients: pasta, chicken, lemon, butter, salt, pepper
directions: Cook pasta and chicken. Mix with butter, lemon, salt, and pepper. Serve warm.

name: Chocolate Chip Muffins
ingredients: flour, sugar, chocolate chips, butter, egg, milk, salt
directions: Mix all ingredients. Spoon into muffin tins. Bake at 350°F for 18-20 minutes. Serve warm.
